snippet.title: [GOTY 2018 #15] Best VGM 2250 - Bloodstained : Curse of the Moon - Stage 2 ~ Frigid Hell
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC / Switch / PS4 / XB1 / Vita / 3DS
Bloodstained : Curse of the Moon (2018)
Stage 2 ~ Frigid Hell
Michiru Yamane
